reviewText:
Episodes:
  Patrick-Man! / Garys New Toy (SpongeBob SquarePants)
  I Think His Name is Baxter Stockman (Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles)
  Muscle C.O.P.S. / Cold Hard Cash (Sanjay and Craig)

This is a DVD full of three different Nickelodeon characters:  Sanjay and Craig, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, and SpongeBob Squarepants.  It contains two episodes of each show and is perfect to get your child's Nickelodeon fix for when their favorite shows are not on.
